Class MaxTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions.BaseAggregateFunction

        • org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions.MaxTime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AggregateFunction, TemporalAggregateFunction
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MaxEdgeTime, MaxVertexTime

    public class MaxTime
extends AbstractTimeAggregateFunction
    Base class for calculating the maximum of a field of a time-interval for temporal elements. If the dimension TimeDimension.VALID_TIME is used for aggregation, this function ignores the default values (TemporalElement.DEFAULT_TIME_FROM and TemporalElement.DEFAULT_TIME_TO) and handles it the same way as null.
